      <title>智利总统加布里埃尔·博里奇提出堕胎和安乐死合法化计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/chile-s-boric-lays-out-plans-to-legalize-abortion-and-euthanasia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利总统加布里埃尔·博里奇表示，他将提出一项彻底合法化堕胎的法案，并将加速对安乐死提案的辩论，这两项计划在分裂的国会中都面临着艰难的批准战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/chile-s-boric-lays-out-plans-to-legalize-abortion-and-euthanasia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 19:22:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《信贷周刊》：贷款狂潮掩盖了违约损失的增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/loan-frenzy-masks-rising-losses-on-defaults-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，企业利用现金追逐信贷的机会，出售了创纪录数量的杠杆贷款。然而，从违约的回收率来看，这类债务的风险正在不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/loan-frenzy-masks-rising-losses-on-defaults-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>未经测试的 ETF 被推销给投资者以对冲全球混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/untested-etfs-pitched-to-investors-as-hedge-against-global-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东和欧洲的战争、中美紧张局势、气候变化、新技术带来的威胁——地缘政治风险无处不在。一群基金经理正在推销一类 ETF，声称可以为所有这些不确定性提供对冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/untested-etfs-pitched-to-investors-as-hedge-against-global-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
